@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home";
}
<div id="page-wrapper">
    <!-- Intro -->
    <section id="intro" class="wrapper style1">
        <div class="title">Who we are</div>
        <div class="container">
            <p class="style1"> Premium Gifts Crafter</p>
            <p class="style3">
                We specialize in limited collections of handmade Premium gifts and flowers.
                We also collaborate with customers to customize and create unique items best represent their love.
            </p>
            <ul class="actions">
                <li><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Flowers" class="button style3 large">Shop flower bouquet</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main -->
    <section id="main" class="wrapper style2">
        <div class="title">Why Buy From Us?</div>
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Features -->
            <section id="features">
                <div class="feature-list">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
                            <section>
                                <h3>Fresh, high-quality flowers</h3>
                                <p>Our flower shop is known for sourcing only the freshest, most beautiful flowers. When you buy from us, you can trust that you're getting a top-notch product that will brighten up any space.</p>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
                            <section>
                                <h3>Variety of flowers</h3>
                                <p>At our flower shop, we offer a wide variety of blooms to suit every taste and occasion. From classic roses to mixed flowers, our selection of flowers is sure to impress. Whether you're looking for a specific type of flower or just want to browse our selection and see what catches your eye, we've got you covered.</p>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
                            <section>
                                <h3>Personalized service</h3>
                                <p>We believe that every customer deserves personalized service, which is why we take the time to get to know your preferences and needs. Whether you're shopping for a special occasion or just looking to brighten up your home, we'll help you find the perfect bouquet.</p>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-12-medium">
                            <section>
                                <h3>Beautiful arrangements</h3>
                                <p>We take pride in creating stunning, unique flower arrangements that you won't find anywhere else. Whether you're looking for a classic bouquet or something more creative and artistic, we've got you covered.</p>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Images -->
                    <div class="uk-child-width-1-2@s uk-child-width-1-3@m" uk-grid="masonry: true" style="margin-top:100px;">
                        <div>
                            <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-flex uk-flex-center uk-flex-middle fill" style="height: 440px">
                                <img src="~/css//images/Tender Heart (1).jpg" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-flex uk-flex-center uk-flex-middle fill" style="height: 500px">
                                <img src="~/css//images/Glitter Harmony (1).jpg" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-flex uk-flex-center uk-flex-middle fill" style="height: 550px">
                                <img src="~/css//images/Night Queen (1).jpg" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Highlights -->
    <section id="highlights" class="wrapper style3">
        <div class="title">How to order</div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row aln-center">
                <div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
                    <section class="highlight">
                        <img src="images/pic02.jpg" alt="" />
                        <h3>1. Call us on WhatsApp</h3>
                        <p>
                            Please reach out to us via WhatsApp with your name along with the bouquet or gifts you are interested.<br />
                            <a href="http://wa.link/zadzlz">Click here to open WhatsApp</a>
                        </p>
                    </section>
                </div>
                <div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
                    <section class="highlight">
                        <img src="images/pic02.jpg" alt="" />
                        <h3>2. Let us know your special occasion</h3>
                        <p>All our gifts are customizable to your needs. Let us know if you have any special requests.</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
                <div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
                    <section class="highlight">
                        <img src="images/pic02.jpg" alt="" />
                        <h3>3. Set your pickup date!</h3>
                        <p>Once your pickup date is confirmed, your gift will be made for ready to pick up!</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

